cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.GR, cs.AI, cs.LG. 

The paper deals with transforming videos into comics using neural style transfer algorithms based on GANs. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves image aesthetic estimation, which falls under cs.MM (Multimedia). The use of keyframe extraction algorithms and the final implementation of a web-based application suggest that the paper may also belong to cs.GR (Graphics) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the use of GANs for style transfer indicates that the paper may also fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning).
